attr.title: Tamiku
attr.desc: Help Tamiku to break all the balloons in the universe in this action-packed platform.
attr.inst: Purchase the game from steam or itch.io. Download the game and place all the gamefiles into ports/tamiku/gamedata

Purchase the game from [steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/1117890/Tamiku/)or [itch.io](https://josyan.itch.io/tamiku)
